# Large binaries (videos + checkpoints): Git/GitHub are poor fits — huge clones, slow history,
# and GitHub blocks files >100MB. Keep code + docs in git; back up artifacts to cloud storage,
# Hugging Face, or a Release zip before terminating a cloud instance.
artifacts/**/*.mp4
artifacts/**/videos/
*.pt
*.pth
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.venv/
# Local backup tarballs from scripts/backup_portfolio.sh
backups/
